title: Peagreen Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Salad bar, Take-out, Bakery, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A wholefood cafe where everything is baked in-house. Offers a daily vegan soup. A mezze platter includes a couple types of houmous & dips, salads, olives, and wholemeal pita. Has a veggie sausage, a prepared salads bar, one daily vegan special. Uses up-cycled furnishing.
